info.name: LilyB's - deviantART
info.description: DeviantART with a muted grey color scheme and pale yellow and green trimmings; browse and view art more comfortably with a neutral background. The screen shot is of an older layout but the color scheme is still the same.
info.additionalInfo:
If there are any pages that seem broken and don't look good please tell me. I don't use DA that much so there are pages that I don't even know exist. Telling me about a page is much more likely to get it fixed than waiting for me to find it.

I really should keep a changelog:
Jan 2, 2015:
Added the tag page. Thanks krinny_userstyle

Nov 16:
   Darkened the 'add a comment' text box.
   Somehow the speech bubble on comments got rotated.
      Re-uploaded that image.
   Added a rule to make reading text on 404, 503, etc. pages easier.

Nov 9:
   Recolored a few pagination links.
   Edited the about DA page.
   Removed a few redundant lines.
   Probably added a few redundant links (of a different kind).

Oct 31
   fixed a search box image.
   Added the Help page.

Oct 28
   Fixed an image that broke.
   Recolored a few journal moduale links that were blue.
   Other small recolors on the profile page.
   Included Settings page.

Oct 26
   Added some of those new profile sections to the theme.
   Added some older proflie sections i had previously missed.
   Fixed daily deviations page alternating background.

Oct 25
   Added support for the message center.
   Theme should be compatible with most public areas of DA.
   All images are now .gifs for bandwidth issues.
